			<h3 class="first"><a href="#p90"></a></h3>
			<p class="author"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=90&amp;sid=6e7acff56ddaaca4c3f8158d89a93dd7#p90"><img src="./styles/prosilver/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="11" height="9" alt="Mensagem" title="Mensagem" /></a>por <strong><a href="./memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=60&amp;sid=6e7acff56ddaaca4c3f8158d89a93dd7" style="color: #000066;" class="username-coloured">nikescar</a></strong> &raquo; 30 Mar 2011, 09:08 </p>

			

			<div class="content"><p>This is a thread for suggestions and questions to make the engine more user friendly. The idea is that these can either be changed in the game engine or the clarification can be included in the tutorials.</p><br /><p>This isn't necessarily a troubleshooting thread.<br /></p><br /></div>

			

		</div>

		
			<dl class="postprofile" id="profile90">
			<dt>
				<a href="./memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=60&amp;sid=6e7acff56ddaaca4c3f8158d89a93dd7"><img src="./download/file.php?avatar=60_1302483748.jpg" width="160" height="175" alt="Avatar do usuário" /></a><br />
